            "body": "Error is throw from `nvim_open_win`, fzf-lua xpcall to catch the error and print the verbose stacktrace.\n```lua\nvim.o.verbose = 1\nvim.cmd([[autocmd BufWinEnter * echoerr 1]])\nlocal buf = vim.api.nvim_create_buf(false, true)\nlocal ok, err = pcall(vim.api.nvim_open_win, buf, false, {\n  style = 'minimal',\n  relative = 'cursor',\n  row = 0,\n  col = 1,\n  height = 10,\n  width = 10,\n})\n-- print(err)\n```",
